                        <xs:documentation source="CalculationsAndRules">Calculated field: 
If  F03_IsAlterrnativePoolPumpFlowResultProvided == true Then 
If F13_PoolReturnLineFlowRate LTE 8 And F14_PoolSuctionLineFlowRate LTE 6 Then result = true;  
Else result = false.
End If
ElseIf F03_IsAlterrnativePoolPumpFlowResultProvided == false Then 
If F09_PoolReturnPipeDiameter GTE F08a_PoolReturnPipeDiameterMinimumRequired And 
F10_PoolSuctionPipeDiameter GTE F08b_PoolSuctionPipeDiameterMinimumRequired And
F11_PoolFilterSurfaceArea GTE F08c_PoolFilterSurfaceAreaMinimumRequired And 
F12_PumpFlowMaximum LTE F08d_PumpFlowMaximumRequired Then result = true; 
Else result = false.  
End If
End If
For Boolean true value display term: System complies.  For Boolean false value display term  System does not comply.</xs:documentation>
                        
                     
